Alas, at the time, I just saw someone confused and a little hurt. I thought that I was seeing past the anger in the post to the hopeful person within.  It's my fault for not seeing that beyond the surface anger in your post, there was more ... anger.  I responded as I would to anyone else coming to this server as I feel that good people adding to the server is a good thing.  I had no idea that the moment you were in the door, you would begin not as a champion of good, which you stylize your character as, but rather a champion of intolerance. <br>
<br>
